== Ubuzima Bwohambere ==
Willine Ikirezi yatangiye 'Daily Healing Voice' muri 2020 nyuma yo guhura nibibazo byubuzima bwo mumutwe. Yahisemo gufasha bagenzi be bahuye nabyo, binyuze mumagambo ya buri munsi.<ref>https://www.newtimes.co.rw/entertainment/dealing-mental-illness-pushed-poet-use-art-help-others</ref>

Mu ntangiriro, yandikaga inyandiko kuri terefone akayishyira ku mbuga nkoranyambaga. Icyo gihe, yari ijambo rimwe kumunsi<ref>https://www.newtimes.co.rw/entertainment/dealing-mental-illness-pushed-poet-use-art-help-others</ref>. Amaze kubona ibitekerezo byinshi kubantu batandukanye yatangiye kwandika imirongo itatu kumunsi no gukoresha amabara ye yerekana, umuhondo numweru, kuri cote. Umuhondo ugereranya ibyiza n'ibyishimo, mugihe umweru ugereranya ubunyangamugayo mubuzima bwa buri wese.<ref>https://www.newtimes.co.rw/entertainment/dealing-mental-illness-pushed-poet-use-art-help-others</ref>

